OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1777306270
OL,3,CWomen's Six Nations: Wales lose 62-24
OL,4,Cto England
OL,6,FEngland roared out of the blocks and
OL,7,Fwent ahead with just six minutes gone
OL,8,Fwhen Feaunati's break took her side
OL,9,Fdeep into the Welsh 22 and she
OL,10,Feventually went over from close range
OL,11,Fwith Helena Rowland adding the
OL,12,Fconversion.
OL,14,FDavid made her mark six minutes later,
OL,15,Fcollecting Holly Aitchison's long pass
OL,16,Fbefore racing away to touch down,
OL,17,Falthough the 20-year-old winger's big
OL,18,Fday would end prematurely after she
OL,19,Ffailed a head injury assessment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
